text: "Big Energy" is a song recorded by American rapper Latto. It was released on September 24, 2021, as a single from her album 777 (2022). It samples American singer-songwriter Mariah Carey's 1995 single "Fantasy", which samples the Tom Tom Club song "Genius of Love" (1981). The song topped Billboard's Mainstream Top 40/Pop Songs radio chart. A remix featuring Carey and DJ Khaled was released on March 28, 2022, and helped the song reach number three on the US Billboard Hot 100. ==Charts== Chart (2021â€“22) Peak position ==References== Category:2021 songs Category:Hip hop songs Category:Mariah Carey songs
